Increment/Decrement Operators:
x++ : Use value, then add 1
++x : Add 1, then use value
x-- : Use value, then subtract 1
--x : Subtract 1, then use value

Steps:
1. Initialize potion_count = 5
2. Print initial value
3. Use post-increment (x++)
4. Use pre-increment (++x)
5. Use post-decrement (x--)
6. Use pre-decrement (--x)

Expected output:
Initial potion count: 5
Post-increment: 5 (now 6)
Pre-increment: 7
Post-decrement: 7 (now 6)
Pre-decrement: 5 